abstract: "Companion code for Digital Rendering Engineering: The Hardware of Light (Volume 2). Includes validated HLSL implementations of DirectX Raytracing (DXR) pipeline, ReSTIR DI/GI, SVGF denoising, Gaussian Splatting, Neural Radiance Cache, and GPU architecture optimizations. Requires Volume 1 companion code."
