  - GPU-architecture
  - HLSL
  - Shader-Model-6.6
  - ray-tracing
  - acceleration-structures
  - BVH
  - render-graph
  - bindless-descriptors
  - Gaussian-Splatting
  - Neural-Radiance-Cache
